scheduler.task.unscheduled

Class UnscheduledTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • scheduler.task.Task
      • scheduler.task.unscheduled.UnscheduledTask
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnscheduledAppointment, UnscheduledMedicalTest, UnscheduledTaskTestClass, UnscheduledTreatment

    public abstract class UnscheduledTask
extends Task
    This class represents a Task that can't immediately be scheduled at system runtime.
